<title>UnicapgtkDeviceSelection</title>
<indexterm zone="UnicapgtkDeviceSelection-struct"><primary>UnicapgtkDeviceSelection</primary></indexterm><programlisting>typedef struct _UnicapgtkDeviceSelection UnicapgtkDeviceSelection;</programlisting>
